📌 Responsive Todo App
🚀 Overview

Excited to share my latest project—a fully responsive Todo App built with React, Vite, and Tailwind CSS! This app provides a clean, intuitive UI to efficiently manage tasks and boost productivity.

🔥 Features:
✅ Add, Edit, and Delete Todos
✅ Mark Todos as Completed
✅ Local Storage Support (Tasks persist after refresh)
✅ Responsive Design (Optimized for mobile & desktop)
✅ Modern UI with React Icons

🛠 Tech Stack:

Frontend: React 19, Vite, Tailwind CSS
State Management: useState, useEffect
Icons: React Icons
Storage: LocalStorage
Linting: ESLint
🏗 Setup & Installation:

bash
Copy
Edit
# Clone the Repository  
git clone https://github.com/AhmadFazel786/todo-app.git  
cd todo-app  

# Install Dependencies  
npm install  

# Run the Development Server  
npm run dev  

# Build for Production  
npm run build  


💡 How to Use:
1️⃣ Enter a task in the input field and click "Save"
2️⃣ Click the checkbox to mark a task as completed
3️⃣ Use the edit button to modify a task
4️⃣ Click the delete button to remove a task
5️⃣ Use the "Show Finished" checkbox to toggle completed tasks

